Una. Nalunaiqsilauqtuq mailimik. Hiuri, hiuri, hiuri.”
Takuminaqtummariulauqpuq qanuq takuksautittijunnarmangaaq taikkuninga kigutinik takuminaqtunik
Uqallanngikkaluaqtillugu.
